overview: Lady Lash Hip hop/Jazz MC of Aboriginal and Greek decent is a creative mother and songstress who will take you on a journey. From the streets of Melbourne in her DIY guerrilla style sound booth to wild ocean, sea scrub and red sandy earth of Kokatha country for womenâ€™s business (far west coast -South Australia). Lady Lash inspired by her connection to country is rewriting her narrative, breaking stereotypes and singing up a storm of creative fusion.
title: Lady Lash
